OL,3,CTamar Bridge tolls set to increase
OL,4,Cdespite warnings a hike would be
OL,5,C'unjust'
OL,7,FCrossing the Tamar Bridge could soon
OL,8,Fcost 15% more.
OL,10,FFollowing a debate at New County Hall
OL,11,Fin Truro, Cornwall councillors have
OL,12,Fnarrowly voted in favour of increasing
OL,13,Fthe bridge tolls.
OL,15,FThe final vote was 38 in favour of
OL,16,Fincreasing the tolls and 36 against.
