OL,3,CTamar Bridge tolls set to increase
OL,4,Cdespite warnings a hike would be
OL,5,C'unjust'
OL,7,FIt would mean cars will have to pay #3
OL,8,Fto cross, rising from #2.60. People
OL,9,Fusing the pre-paid electronic tag
OL,10,Fsystem have to pay #1.50, rising from
OL,11,F#1.30.
OL,13,FA number of councillors spoke about
OL,14,Fthe economic impact on people in the
OL,15,FDuchy, particularly in the south east
OL,16,Fand eastern parts of Cornwall.
OL,18,FOne even described it as an "unfair
OL,19,Fand unjust tax on the people of
OL,20,FCornwall".
