OL,3,CTamar Bridge tolls set to increase
OL,4,Cdespite warnings a hike would be
OL,5,C'unjust'
OL,7,FHowever the council's Conservative
OL,8,Fportfolio holder for transport Cllr
OL,9,FRichard Williams-Pears said the
OL,10,Fdecision had to be made due to
OL,11,Ffinancial pressures resulting from
OL,12,Fcontinued reduced traffic flows post-
OL,13,FCovid and high inflation levels since
OL,14,Fthe outbreak of war in Ukraine.
OL,16,FThe council heard that without
OL,17,Fintervention, "forecast income will be
OL,18,Finsufficient to support the continued
OL,19,Fdelivery of safe reliable and
OL,20,Fefficient crossings".
