OL,7,FA statement from Saltash Lib Dem
OL,8,Fcouncillor Hilary Frank was read out
OL,9,Fat the meeting. She said the increase
OL,10,Fwould have significant financial
OL,11,Fimplications for residents of the town
OL,12,Fas well as the whole of south east
OL,13,FCornwall and said it was akin to
OL,14,F"daylight robbery", which represents a
OL,15,F50 per cent uplift on what people were
OL,16,Fpaying in December 2022.
