OL,7,FConservative councillor Philip
OL,8,FDesmonde called the tolls an
OL,9,F"unacceptable tax on businesses and
OL,10,Fresidents" and called for National
OL,11,FHighways to pay a contribution as the
OL,12,FTamar bridge carries the A38.
OL,13,FIndependent councillor Paul Wills
OL,14,Fcalled the tolls an "unfair and unjust
OL,15,Ftax on the people of Cornwall".
