OL,5,C'unjust'
OL,7,FIn a heartfelt speech, Jane Pascoe,
OL,8,FConservative councillor for Liskeard
OL,9,FSouth and Dobwalls, added: "I cannot
OL,10,Fsupport further increase to the Tamar
OL,11,Ftolls. The impact on hard-working
OL,12,Fpeople in south east Cornwall and east
OL,13,FCornwall should never be
OL,14,Funderestimated.
OL,16,F"These are not anonymous people ` they
OL,17,Fare Cornish residents, some are
OL,18,Fnurses, porters, dockyard workers,
OL,19,Fteachers and shop assistants.
OL,26,@qD@\OU
