OL,3,CTamar Bridge tolls set to increase
OL,4,Cdespite warnings a hike would be
OL,5,C'unjust'
OL,7,F"They are people who are struggling to
OL,8,Fbring up a family, pay mortgages, high
OL,9,Fenergy bills and fuel costs. We can do
OL,10,Ffar better for them. For their sake we
OL,11,Fmust all try harder to solve the
OL,12,Fproblem of the maintenance of the
OL,13,FTamar crossings.
OL,15,F"The tolls mean people in south east
OL,16,FCornwall must pay to access hospital
OL,17,Ftreatment and to go to work and school
OL,18,For college. Those people should no
OL,19,Flonger shoulder the burden of
OL,20,Fmaintaining the bridge and the ferry."
